== Introduction ==
The Artwork Strike Force, or ASF, is purposed to contribute artwork to the <nowiki>[[UbuntuMediaCenterTeam|Ubuntu Media Center]]</nowiki> project. The primary areas of activity include artwork for <nowiki>[[http://elisa.fluendo.com/|Elisa]]</nowiki> and the <nowiki>[[http://www.ubuntumediacenter.org/|Ubuntu Media Center]]</nowiki> distribution.

== Current Activities ==
* <nowiki>[[Media_Center_Artwork|Ubuntu Media Center Logo Design]]</nowiki>
* <nowiki>[[http://www.ubuntumediacenter.org/|Website]]</nowiki> Artwork

== Members ==
* Christophe Dumas (leader)
* <nowiki>[[https://launchpad.net/~philippe-normand|Phillipe Normand]]</nowiki> (leader)
